    <thetext>+++ This bug was initially created as a clone of Bug #1404450 +++

While debugging another problem on F25 Atomic Host, I was trying to find a way to disable the &apos;oci-register-machine&apos; hook.  It appears the only way to do so is to remove the hook from &apos;/usr/libexec/oci/hooks.d/&apos;

However, on an Atomic Host the /usr filesystem is read-only and can&apos;t be modified.

I think we need a way to disable this hook (and any others) on an Atomic Host.</thetext>
